      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 19.2) is a commercially validated code with documented QA procedures, release notes, and version control. All simulation scripts are archived in a traceable repository consistent with MRL 2 requirements."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
