      "rationale": "The FDA generic centrifugal pump is a widely accepted surrogate for Class II CPB pump geometries. The validation flow conditions (Reynolds number range, non-Newtonian blood analogue) are representative of clinical CPB operating envelopes, supporting applicability of validation evidence to the intended decision."
    },
